    <dd>Is auto-registration of virtual machine records in the virtual network in the Private DNS zone enabled?</dd><dt class="property-"

        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd>The resolution policy on the virtual network link. Only applicable for virtual network links to privatelink zones, and for A,AAAA,CNAME queries.
